ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAGREEMENT - Bring into force Bahamas FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Commonwealth of The BAHAMAS FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS, signed in The Bahamas on 17 June 2010.
